snippet.title: The Sims 4 Perfect Patio Stuff: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Add hot tubs to create the perfect outdoor space for your Sim’s home with The Sims 4 Perfect Patio Stuff!
 
Learn more about this Stuff Pack: http://o.ea.com/39191
 
Includes the all-new hot tub that handy Sims can upgrade to include a stereo and even aromatherapy.
